{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_qu_ao","speaker_name":"曲傲","listener":null,"text":"牵马！傍我押阵！","tone":"沉声","chapter":188,"line_start":27,"line_end":27},{"speaker":"char_zhang_shu_mou","speaker_name":"长叔谋","listener":"char_qu_ao","text":"师尊何用理会他，待我们把他收拾便行！","tone":"疑问","chapter":188,"line_start":29,"line_end":29},{"speaker":"char_qu_ao","speaker_name":"曲傲","listener":null,"text":"不必多言，看我先把此子宰了。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":188,"line_start":49,"line_end":51},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":"char_qu_ao","text":"曲傲你枉称铁勒的武学大师，却只能在以众凌寡的情况下对付我们，此等行径心术，不怕教天下人耻笑吗？","tone":"豪迈","chapter":188,"line_start":61,"line_end":63},{"speaker":"char_qu_ao","speaker_name":"曲傲","listener":"char_ba_feng_han","text":"当日我孤身一人追杀你们三个小子，可又谁是众谁是寡？只为防范你等仍照惯例落荒而逃，才作了点布置手段！小子你如若这么看不开，最好便不要出来浑，免致丢人现眼。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":188,"line_start":65,"line_end":71},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":"char_qu_ao","text":"以前只因你尚未摸清楚我们的实力，跋某人有说错吗？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":188,"line_start":73,"line_end":75},{"speaker":"char_qu_ao","speaker_name":"曲傲","listener":"char_ba_feng_han","text":"何来这么多废话，你既打定主意送死，便让我来为你完成心愿。","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":188,"line_start":79,"line_end":81},{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":"char_qu_ao","text":"曲傲你尚未够资格成为跋某人的真正大敌，只能是我挑战毕玄的踏脚石，动手吧！","tone":"淡然","chapter":188,"line_start":83,"line_end":85}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_ba_feng_han","name":"跋锋寒","alias":[],"identity":"铁勒高手，独行剑客","faction":"无","role":"companion","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"铁勒族出身的天才剑客，曾败于毕玄后奋发图强，与寇仲徐子陵结为挚友","personality":{"traits":["豪迈","坚韧","自信","冷酷","好战","重义"],"speech_style":"直率犀利，言语锋利如剑","temperament":"外冷内热，战意高昂"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_qu_ao","type":"宿敌","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"从对手到敬佩"},{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"挚友","intensity":85,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"并肩作战"},{"target":"char_xu_zi_ling","type":"挚友","intensity":85,"bond_level":